window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>An action-packed LitRPG Adventure perfect for fans of Mother of Learning, Skill-Grinder, and The Perfect Run!</i></p> <p><b>Break the Baseline. Break the Limits.</b></p> <p>Once upon a time, a mageblade-in-training lost his best friend. His soul refused to let her go, and his unformed soulspell developed the ability to revert the timeline to the week before her death. It wasn't enough. No matter what he did, said, or tried, her death was set in stone. He was too poor, too weak, too powerless.</p> <p>Some things even perfection cannot accomplish. So he moved forward, over and over again. Saved the world a few times. Refined himself into a power few could match.</p> <p>Yet the moment he reverted, he'd be trapped in the same powerless, ineffective body he'd started out with. Never enough. Nothing ever changed.</p> <p>Until now.</p> <p><b>Experience this fast-paced, time-loop LitRPG Adventure featuring a detailed system, loads of skills, time loop regression, an overpowered Magic Sword as the catalyst for change, slow-build power progression, and so much more!</b></p>"; 
